post_text:
Last May the Oregon Legislature passed the Student Success Act (SSA). This law will provide new funding to Oregon schools. We have developed a survey asking for your ideas for how we should spend these new funds. If you have not already had the opportunity to complete it we would like to encourage you to take the time to fill it out by January 20th. We are very interested in your ideas about how we can better serve our students.



Here is a link to the survey. https://corbett.k12.or.us/survey

If you would prefer a paper copy or have any questions please contact Holly Dearixon hdearixon@corbett.k12.or.us
